<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Evade..<p>

This skill causes a mob to attack who ever has it in its aggro list, it is sort of like the opposite of taunt for rogues, to use the skill you just stop attacking and hide, if it works it will attack whoever is also attacking, but I have noticed it doesn't always work on all mobs, for like Ghouls in Lower Guk, successfully evaded many times and doesn't seem to effect them at all. Evade works great to keep the mob on the tank while you keep backstabbing, what I do is evade after every backstab to make sure the mob stays off me, but I don't suggest evading if you are the only melee in your group, and evade doesn't do anything while soloing, since it is used to make mob attack someone else who is attacking it.<p>

I am lvl 38 with 139 str using SBD, and my max backstab is 147 damage.<p>

Jeckie Chan of Veeshan<br>
level 38 Wood Elf Rogue</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
